  "text": "We also mean-center the variables forming interaction term to avoid the problem of multicollinearity [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The descriptive statistics and correlation matrix are presented in Tables 2 and 3 . With respect to our main variables of interest we find that cognitive abilities are strongly correlated with life satisfaction, while the correlation between government size and SWB is very moderate (Table 3 ). In addition the correlations reported in Table 3 do not suggest any potential multicollinearity problem in our empirical exercise.",
